<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&lt;input type
                ="number"&gt;</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">元素可以帮助您在构建用户界面和将数字输入到表单中的逻辑时简化你的工作。
                当你使用正确的</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">
                type </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">值</span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;"> "number"
            </span></span><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">创建数字输入时，会自动验证你输入的文本是否为数字，通常是一组向上和向下按钮。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type:disc">
    <li><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span
                style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">浏览器可能会选择提供步进箭头，让用户可以使用鼠标增加和减少输入的值，或者只需用指尖敲击即可。</span></span>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">&nbsp;</span></span></p>

                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">表示。你可以通过把一个数字放在</span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Comic Sans MS&quot;">value </span><span
                            style="font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;">属性中来设置输入框的默认值</span></span></p>
